{"tid":1446294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議喺8月18號搞番場百萬人大遊行","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:34:08.000Z","uid":156096,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f28f3811cd472bee6e8d792d88af46646358f241","tid":1446294,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"依家班狗已經癲哂，室內放煙、射爆眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、派卧底咩都做齊。<br />\n我建議喺8月18號搞番場百萬人大遊行，要強調和理非，今次要好似6月16號咁，行完就散，等啲人可以帶埋一家大細出黎。宣傳期間，要不斷強調一個死線，例如19號24點前要回應，講明唔無回應就行動升級。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔回應既話，到時我地有百幾萬民意支持，到24/25號，佢地就後果自負。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cb1a75c7dade36ccb7dfb7d91a42e5f7de5a53","tid":1446294,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"推到民陣搞遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477d9fac358268fdb2c8ee9b8094bf12cfeb59e5","tid":1446294,"uid":108806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"02b9843a9e2ada49905bae8a7a0d535b67e02238","tid":1446294,"uid":108806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"edbafc6e81651f4df27ba81802fc301f1e19f1ce","tid":1446294,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\